      "span_text": "The lipid peak at 2 ppm is not significantly attenuated by the SelMQC sequence owing to its coupling with the vinyl peak at 5.3 ppm as previously observed  ; however, this is far enough removed from the lactate peak at 1.3 ppm for it not to interfere with quantification."
